<H3><B><I><CENTER>Part 903<BR>
 
          UNIFORM ACCOUNTING INSTRUCTIONS FOR FIRE AND
             MARINE AND CASUALTY AND SURETY INSURERS
</H3></B></I></CENTER><BR><HR>
 SUBPART A:  RULES RELATING TO OPERATING EXPENSE CLASSIFICATIONS
<P><HR>
