      LIFE    ACCIDENT & HEALTH    PROPERTY    CASUALTY      MOTOR VEHICLE
          LONG-TERM CARE (1)        LONG-TERM CARE PARTNERSHIP (2)
      (1) SPECIFIC CONTENT ESTABLISHED BY 50 ILL. ADM. CODE 2012.
      (2) SPECIFIC CONTENT ESTABLISHED BY 50 ILL. ADM. CODE 2018.


      INSTRUCTION METHOD/HOURS                 EXAMINATION METHOD

  NUMBER OF CLASSROOM HOURS                                SUPERVISED

  NUMBER OF SEMINAR HOURS                                  NON-SUPERVISED

