            STATES                           HOURS APPROVED
                                                                   
                                                                   

We do certify that this course meets all of the applicable requirements of
Part 3119 and that we will maintain and provide students all applicable
records required by Part 3119. We understand that failure to comply with
the requirements of Part 3119 shall result in our disqualification.
